        <mxCell id="leg-note" parent="1" style="text;html=1;fontSize=11;align=left;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#555555;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="&lt;b&gt;Note.&lt;/b&gt;  InferenceObjective (x-k8s.io/v1alpha2) carries request priority only — not shown here to keep the flow clean.&#xa;Model dispatch is done by BBR header injection + HTTPRoute match, &lt;b&gt;NOT&lt;/b&gt; by the deprecated InferenceModel.modelName API.&#xa;HF_TOKEN (Secret hf-token) lets vLLM Pods pull Gemma weights from Hugging Face at startup." vertex="1">
